::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:center
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:19.440
One Piece

3
00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:19.440
Wano Arc

4
00:01:42.170 --> 00:01:46.420
<b>Mummy</b>

5
00:01:47.460 --> 00:01:50.090
Seize Straw Hat Luffy!

6
00:01:52.470 --> 00:01:54.430
Here they come!

7
00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:58.640
Imagine the haki...

8
00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.350
flowing through my body.

9
00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:04.150
You're mine!

10
00:02:09.770 --> 00:02:11.440
That's not it!

11
00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:15.320
Go to hell!

12
00:02:25.140 --> 00:02:26.920
It's so weird...!

13
00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:28.980
That wasn't it!

14
00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:34.380
This surface-level haki won't
be enough to bring down Kaido.

15
00:02:35.020 --> 00:02:38.050
I've gotta get the haki
to flow into my enemies...

16
00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:43.180
If I could get the haki to flow...

17
00:02:44.090 --> 00:02:48.310
I could even smash through Kaido's thick skin.

18
00:02:49.190 --> 00:02:51.320
Oops! I pushed too hard!

19
00:02:52.050 --> 00:02:53.240
You've done it now!

20
00:03:00.730 --> 00:03:04.140
Damn! That's just not it!

21
00:03:04.790 --> 00:03:05.710
But...

22
00:03:07.250 --> 00:03:10.670
I've still got plenty of sparring partners.

23
00:03:10.670 --> 00:03:14.640
I won't stop until I master ryuo!

24
00:03:17.610 --> 00:03:21.310
Sir Straw Hat sure is a persistent man.

25
00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:23.600
Let's go, Chopperemon!

26
00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:24.770
Okay.

27
00:03:24.770 --> 00:03:26.220
To rescue Olin!

28
00:03:26.220 --> 00:03:26.980
What?!

29
00:03:26.980 --> 00:03:32.180
No way! Don't worry about Olin!
I'm glad she's gone!

30
00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:34.690
We need to help Luffytaro, Kiku!

31
00:03:35.370 --> 00:03:37.610
Why won't he run already?

32
00:03:37.610 --> 00:03:39.370
Let's go!

33
00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:39.370
Certainly!

34
00:03:39.370 --> 00:03:45.080
Warden, should I throw the prisoners
in their cells before they get any ideas?

35
00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.110
Good thinking.

36
00:03:48.420 --> 00:03:50.900
Luffytaro is something else.

37
00:03:50.900 --> 00:03:53.090
Yeah, he's a powerhouse.

38
00:03:53.090 --> 00:03:55.320
This might be the moment...

39
00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:58.380
The guards are stretched thin...
It's now or never!

40
00:03:59.530 --> 00:04:01.140
No need to worry.

41
00:04:01.140 --> 00:04:03.560
Counter poison with poison.

42
00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:06.430
Daifugo, it's time for you-know-what.

43
00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:10.370
You-know-what, huh? Got it...

44
00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:17.240
Prisoners, listen carefully!

45
00:04:17.770 --> 00:04:21.870
Your fellow prisoner Luffytaro is
out of control and making trouble.

46
00:04:21.870 --> 00:04:24.830
You know what that means, right?

47
00:04:25.550 --> 00:04:27.120
What is he talking about?!

48
00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:41.430
Go do everything you can
to restrain Luffytaro!

49
00:04:41.430 --> 00:04:45.770
Huh? You've gotta be kidding.
There's no way they'll listen to you.

50
00:04:45.770 --> 00:04:46.520
What?

51
00:04:54.020 --> 00:04:56.480
Wh-Wh-Whaaat?!

52
00:04:56.480 --> 00:05:00.450
Stop it! I'm on your side!

53
00:05:00.450 --> 00:05:02.820
Do you wanna escape or what?!

54
00:05:02.820 --> 00:05:06.440
Well, we've had it with the guards!

55
00:05:06.440 --> 00:05:11.250
I admit I was thrilled
when I saw you rampaging!

56
00:05:11.250 --> 00:05:16.130
But escaping from here won't bring
Kaido and Orochi's reign to an end!

57
00:05:19.170 --> 00:05:24.010
We fought to avenge
Lord Kozuki Oden's death!

58
00:05:24.010 --> 00:05:25.890
But that pirate Kaido...

59
00:05:25.890 --> 00:05:31.890
...slaughtered our families and friends
and beat us into submission!

60
00:05:33.770 --> 00:05:36.790
Lord Yasuie's execution

61
00:05:36.790 --> 00:05:40.780
brought back the fear and despair
of our past failure.

62
00:05:40.780 --> 00:05:46.330
We leave here, and we've got
nowhere to go and nothing to eat.

63
00:05:46.330 --> 00:05:51.500
There's no liberty anywhere
in this country anymore!

64
00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:57.880
That's right! You might as well lay low here!

65
00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:00.320
Don't be so selfish!

66
00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:03.010
You're the one being selfish!

67
00:06:03.010 --> 00:06:08.890
Since you're a stranger from overseas, run away or fight all you want...

68
00:06:08.890 --> 00:06:11.900
but leave us out of it from here on!

69
00:06:12.980 --> 00:06:19.940
Don't give us any more false hope, dammit!

70
00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.170
You guys...

71
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:29.400
Are you all right?

72
00:06:29.400 --> 00:06:31.050
Hey, stay with us!

73
00:06:34.430 --> 00:06:38.880
Hey, this is no time for you
to be worrying about others.

74
00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:42.010
Hot... It's so hot...! Help me...!

75
00:06:42.010 --> 00:06:42.660
Whoa!

76
00:06:42.660 --> 00:06:43.670
What's wrong?!

77
00:06:46.950 --> 00:06:48.680
What's this crap?!

78
00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.600
I told you to worry about yourselves!

79
00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:57.060
It's a contagious plague.
Touch it and you'll get it.

80
00:07:02.940 --> 00:07:05.170
They're an example to the rest of you!

81
00:07:05.170 --> 00:07:08.950
Start acting strange, and I'll
shoot you with an infected round!

82
00:07:10.580 --> 00:07:13.980
His Awesomeness Queen loves his inventions.

83
00:07:13.980 --> 00:07:17.040
It's his hobby to create
mechanical weapons and viruses.

84
00:07:19.930 --> 00:07:21.400
Oh, it's so hot.

85
00:07:22.460 --> 00:07:25.880
Have one of His Awesomeness Queen's...

86
00:07:25.880 --> 00:07:28.090
plague rounds!

87
00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:37.650
Straw Hat, did you really think
the prisoners would fight on your side?!

88
00:07:38.730 --> 00:07:44.240
Too bad we've already broken
their rebellious spirits!

89
00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:47.280
Shut up! You'll never hit me with that!

90
00:07:47.690 --> 00:07:52.660
Look around, idiot! It's gonna spread
regardless of who I hit!

91
00:07:53.540 --> 00:07:56.840
Hey, spread out! We're all gonna get infected!

92
00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:59.250
It doesn't matter.

93
00:07:59.690 --> 00:08:02.880
We'll meet our end here.

94
00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:06.920
Damn! If only I could tell them everything,
they'd change their minds!

95
00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:09.550
It's over, Straw Hat!

96
00:08:16.230 --> 00:08:21.360
Hey, straw hat boy, just let
the fish out of the net already.

97
00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:23.480
Let them know there is hope.

98
00:08:24.510 --> 00:08:29.990
That we have this one last chance
to bring down Kaido.

99
00:08:34.370 --> 00:08:36.650
The voice is coming from the sealed cell.

100
00:08:36.650 --> 00:08:38.840
So that stubborn bastard's still alive...

101
00:08:38.840 --> 00:08:42.400
Warden, wasn't some kind of beast in there?!

102
00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:45.590
That's right, you guys were never told.

103
00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:49.630
There was no beast locked in that cell.

104
00:08:50.500 --> 00:08:55.600
"Kill him by feeding him fish contaminated
with industrial wastewater."

105
00:08:55.600 --> 00:09:00.390
Lord Orochi gave that order thirteen years ago,
intending to execute the bastard.

106
00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:06.110
We couldn't disobey an order
from Lord Orochi, so we let him live.

107
00:09:06.110 --> 00:09:10.320
Really, he should have been executed
ahead of everyone else.

108
00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:13.200
The man in that cell...

109
00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:16.620
is one of the Nine Red Scabbards!

110
00:09:16.620 --> 00:09:18.140
What?! No way!

111
00:09:18.140 --> 00:09:19.790
I thought they were all dead!

112
00:09:20.580 --> 00:09:23.920
So kill him now! We'll
make it look like an accident!

113
00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:26.750
That laugh...

114
00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:28.870
Without a doubt, that is Kawamatsu!

115
00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:29.840
Hey!

116
00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:31.760
Kawamatsu!

117
00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.970
I am on my way!

118
00:09:34.970 --> 00:09:36.760
There he is, the little dirtbag.

119
00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:40.230
He's one of the legendary
Nine Red Scabbards?!

120
00:09:42.310 --> 00:09:44.190
I'll take the credit for the kill!

121
00:09:47.550 --> 00:09:49.440
That really hurts!

122
00:09:50.690 --> 00:09:51.990
What is that? A needle?!

123
00:09:51.990 --> 00:09:54.450
No, it's a fishbone.

124
00:09:54.450 --> 00:09:58.030
<b>Ninpo</b>

125
00:09:54.450 --> 00:09:58.040
Ninpo: Flying Squirrel Technique!

126
00:09:55.330 --> 00:09:58.040
<b>Flying Squirrel</b>

127
00:09:55.780 --> 00:09:55.990
<b>Flying Squirrel Technique</b>

128
00:09:55.990 --> 00:09:57.950
<b>Technique</b>

129
00:10:04.220 --> 00:10:05.590
Oh... Oh, no!

130
00:10:05.590 --> 00:10:07.210
The intruder has escaped!

131
00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:09.670
Kawamatsu!

132
00:10:09.670 --> 00:10:12.970
Here is the key to the cuffs
and your sword!

133
00:10:19.140 --> 00:10:21.770
You're just in time, Raizo!

134
00:10:27.130 --> 00:10:30.160
I've missed you, my beloved sword...

135
00:10:31.420 --> 00:10:33.240
Sotomuso!

136
00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:35.140
Gentlemen...

137
00:10:40.090 --> 00:10:42.620
do you like sumo wrestling?

138
00:10:48.220 --> 00:10:49.460
Kawamatsu...

139
00:10:50.410 --> 00:10:51.300
help is coming!

140
00:10:51.300 --> 00:10:53.670
Ready...!

141
00:10:54.590 --> 00:10:56.840
Go!

142
00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:01.640
Yagura Ryuo!

143
00:11:08.810 --> 00:11:09.770
What the...?

144
00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:11.980
First one to fly loses.

145
00:11:11.980 --> 00:11:16.240
You are still as strong as ever, Kawamatsu.

146
00:11:19.530 --> 00:11:21.380
That technique...

147
00:11:21.380 --> 00:11:22.370
What a relief.

148
00:11:24.210 --> 00:11:25.040
You bastard!

149
00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:30.030
Like swimming in the rapids of a great river.

150
00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:36.500
It is known as

151
00:11:36.500 --> 00:11:38.220
Kappa Style...

152
00:11:40.350 --> 00:11:42.430
River of Retribution!

153
00:11:49.270 --> 00:11:52.980
<b>River of
Retribution</b>

154
00:11:58.100 --> 00:12:01.090
Were those poisoned fish palatable?

155
00:12:01.090 --> 00:12:05.340
Actually, their awful taste
nauseated me and ruined my bowels.

156
00:12:05.340 --> 00:12:09.280
But I stayed alive for thirteen years!

157
00:12:09.280 --> 00:12:13.830
This burden is but a gentle breeze
in light of my grief for my lord.

158
00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:15.390
I have waited for this moment!

159
00:12:15.390 --> 00:12:19.780
Kawamatsu the Kappa has joined the battle!

160
00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:22.930
<b>Yokozuna Kawamatsu

A Kozuki Clan Retainer</b>

161
00:12:22.970 --> 00:12:24.350
Kawamatsu!

162
00:12:25.530 --> 00:12:26.840
Is that Kiku?!

163
00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:30.780
You have not changed a bit!

164
00:12:30.780 --> 00:12:33.680
I am so glad to see you alive!

165
00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:35.420
Raizo, I feel the same.

166
00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:37.780
Huh?! Kiku! When did you arrive?!

167
00:12:37.780 --> 00:12:42.170
What's going on?!
Who's that guy with a giant face?!

168
00:12:42.170 --> 00:12:47.200
He's an intruder! He stole the keys
and the sword from the tower!

169
00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:51.550
What the hell are you waiting for?!
Seize them already!

170
00:12:51.550 --> 00:12:53.170
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

171
00:13:04.250 --> 00:13:07.520
What the hell did you come back for?!

172
00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:09.310
Kawamatsu...

173
00:13:09.310 --> 00:13:11.830
Are you okay, my friend?

174
00:13:13.190 --> 00:13:16.940
I must apologize. I feel I am about
to lose thirteen years of lunches.

175
00:13:20.860 --> 00:13:25.330
Prepare the plague rounds!
Let's finish them off!

176
00:13:25.730 --> 00:13:28.120
Everyone, prepare for battle!

177
00:13:31.050 --> 00:13:33.080
Step away from Luffytaro!

178
00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:35.920
Kiku! Raizo!

179
00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:37.870
<b>Leopard</b>
<b>HYO</b>

180
00:13:39.990 --> 00:13:42.340
Whoa! Gramps!

181
00:13:43.530 --> 00:13:46.430
What...? Could you really be Boss Hyogoro?!

182
00:13:46.430 --> 00:13:50.770
Indeed. But more importantly... Kiku! Raizo!

183
00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:54.640
Tell them who you are!

184
00:13:55.890 --> 00:14:02.320
There are those with broken spirits,
and there are those who have fought and lost.

185
00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:07.020
If you wish to inspire them, you must
remove those cloth face coverings!

186
00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:10.420
You speak the truth,

187
00:14:10.420 --> 00:14:12.000
Boss Hyogoro.

188
00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:14.250
How right you are.

189
00:14:14.250 --> 00:14:16.630
We must first earn their trust.

190
00:14:18.970 --> 00:14:24.590
If we do not reveal our identities,
we are no more than ghosts...

191
00:14:49.530 --> 00:14:51.500
It can't be...! That mask...!

192
00:14:53.650 --> 00:14:56.670
Wasn't he a warrior who
died at Oden Castle...?

193
00:14:56.670 --> 00:14:59.620
The most beautiful swordsman in Wano...

194
00:15:00.710 --> 00:15:02.880
Kikunojo of the Lingering Snow?!

195
00:15:02.880 --> 00:15:05.510
What?! You're a man?!

196
00:15:06.250 --> 00:15:07.760
I am a woman at heart.

197
00:15:07.760 --> 00:15:09.430
That mask is scary!

198
00:15:10.950 --> 00:15:11.810
And that's...

199
00:15:12.620 --> 00:15:16.770
Fukurokuju's rival ninja, Raizo of the Mist!

200
00:15:16.770 --> 00:15:22.690
And there's the samurai Yokozuna Kawamatsu,
the greatest sumo wrestler of all time!

201
00:15:22.690 --> 00:15:28.660
That old man alongside them must be
the real Hyogoro the Flower!

202
00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:31.950
So...

203
00:15:31.950 --> 00:15:35.410
who the hell is Luffytaro?

204
00:15:38.850 --> 00:15:41.170
Whatever, that's an amazing group!

205
00:15:41.170 --> 00:15:44.210
What?! What about me?!

206
00:15:46.050 --> 00:15:49.680
This has turned out just like
Lord Orochi's ravings!

207
00:15:49.680 --> 00:15:53.430
We've got to warn Viceroy Kaido somehow!

208
00:15:53.430 --> 00:15:53.930
No...

209
00:15:56.050 --> 00:16:01.900
Now that you have seen us,
you will need to stay silent.

210
00:16:05.140 --> 00:16:06.490
Take them down!

211
00:16:10.740 --> 00:16:13.950
Ninpo: Flower Shuriken!

212
00:16:31.510 --> 00:16:34.780
Heavy Gong!

213
00:16:35.970 --> 00:16:38.000
Gum-Gum...

214
00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:40.980
Gatling!

215
00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:47.480
Eat this plague round!

216
00:16:50.910 --> 00:16:51.700
What?!

217
00:16:57.130 --> 00:17:00.560
We can't hit him with the plague rounds,
Vice Warden Daifugo!

218
00:17:00.560 --> 00:17:03.340
I told you idiots it doesn't matter who they hit!

219
00:17:05.690 --> 00:17:09.760
You bastards! First you starve the prisoners,
and now you're shooting them!

220
00:17:10.690 --> 00:17:13.550
I can't let you use a virus as a weapon!

221
00:17:16.340 --> 00:17:19.390
Hold it! We won't let you get
in Vice Warden Daifugo's way!

222
00:17:19.390 --> 00:17:20.920
Let's go, Chopper!

223
00:17:20.920 --> 00:17:21.900
All right!

224
00:17:24.310 --> 00:17:25.940
Gum-Gum...

225
00:17:27.530 --> 00:17:29.780
Heavy Stamp!

226
00:17:34.910 --> 00:17:37.200
Leave our countrymen alone!

227
00:17:46.130 --> 00:17:48.420
As he said!

228
00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:56.390
It's a demon!

229
00:17:56.390 --> 00:17:58.560
Kappa Style...

230
00:18:03.230 --> 00:18:04.980
Yorikiri!

231
00:18:15.490 --> 00:18:18.860
Ninpo: Lightning Shuriken!

232
00:18:40.970 --> 00:18:44.220
Use these, friend of Master Luffy.

233
00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:46.000
Friend?!

234
00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:48.600
One of them should work.

235
00:18:58.020 --> 00:18:59.150
Damn!

236
00:18:59.150 --> 00:19:00.940
I've been shot!

237
00:19:01.730 --> 00:19:04.050
It's hot! It's so hot!

238
00:19:05.070 --> 00:19:07.150
Help me or it'll spread!

239
00:19:07.150 --> 00:19:08.170
Stay away from me!

240
00:19:09.800 --> 00:19:12.050
Ahh, hot, hot, hot!

241
00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:17.360
Damn, those bastards are just
aiming at the prisoners!

242
00:19:25.830 --> 00:19:28.650
Oh, that's right. I forgot to mention one thing.

243
00:19:28.650 --> 00:19:32.070
The disease's name.

244
00:19:34.560 --> 00:19:37.860
A high fever spreads from
where the bullet hits.

245
00:19:38.560 --> 00:19:42.160
Burning pain radiates across the body.

246
00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:42.160
Ahh, it's hot!

247
00:19:42.160 --> 00:19:45.080
Victims spew blood.

248
00:19:45.080 --> 00:19:49.460
Then they suffer and wriggle about...

249
00:19:50.010 --> 00:19:55.340
and infect others with
that pain indiscriminately!

250
00:19:56.210 --> 00:19:58.540
Help me...!

251
00:19:58.540 --> 00:19:59.640
Stop that!

252
00:19:59.640 --> 00:20:01.540
I'm in so much pain...!

253
00:20:01.540 --> 00:20:02.920
Let go!

254
00:20:04.780 --> 00:20:06.230
Behold!

255
00:20:06.230 --> 00:20:10.170
That's what becomes of the infected!

256
00:20:11.600 --> 00:20:14.020
Help me...

257
00:20:18.620 --> 00:20:24.320
They're like dried-up, rotten plants!

258
00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:37.260
Help me...

259
00:20:37.260 --> 00:20:39.200
Stay back. Don't come close.

260
00:20:44.930 --> 00:20:46.700
That's...

261
00:20:47.540 --> 00:20:50.180
His Awesomeness Queen's masterpiece!

262
00:20:50.180 --> 00:20:54.340
This plague is called Mummy!

263
00:21:01.410 --> 00:21:02.450
Go!

264
00:21:03.250 --> 00:21:09.290
You are now human weapons capable
of defeating enemies with a single touch!

265
00:21:10.540 --> 00:21:12.710
We can't let the virus spread!

266
00:21:12.710 --> 00:21:15.510
Everyone, you need to stop moving!

267
00:21:15.510 --> 00:21:17.070
I'll handle this somehow!

268
00:21:17.070 --> 00:21:20.470
I will cure every one of you!

269
00:21:20.470 --> 00:21:22.340
The rest of you should get moving!

270
00:21:22.940 --> 00:21:24.970
Or should I consider you rebels?

271
00:21:30.600 --> 00:21:31.270
Dammit!

272
00:21:34.530 --> 00:21:35.690
They're not stopping!

273
00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:37.570
In the end,

274
00:21:37.570 --> 00:21:41.950
everyone in Udon is against us!

275
00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:45.530
Get outta here!

276
00:21:49.530 --> 00:21:51.920
If you hadn't come...

277
00:21:53.500 --> 00:21:58.050
we'd have never met this fate!

278
00:21:58.050 --> 00:22:01.550
Even if you guys really are...

279
00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:09.720
the Red Scabbard samurai... who were
thought to have died twenty years ago...

280
00:22:09.720 --> 00:22:12.270
you'll never win!

281
00:22:13.730 --> 00:22:15.110
Kaido...!

282
00:22:15.900 --> 00:22:19.480
That giant flying dragon...!

283
00:22:20.710 --> 00:22:23.670
The Beast Pirates...!

284
00:22:23.670 --> 00:22:25.870
No one can defeat them!

285
00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:29.540
Look at us...

286
00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:37.050
Just one of Kaido's subordinates
created this single weapon...

287
00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:40.420
and brought this menace!

288
00:22:42.220 --> 00:22:45.890
Its power is devastating!

289
00:22:47.920 --> 00:22:53.200
That's right! If you strangers hadn't come...

290
00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:57.770
we'd have been able to maintain
our daily routine here in Udon!

291
00:22:59.900 --> 00:23:04.140
We'd have never had to go through this!

292
00:23:16.340 --> 00:23:18.290
No, Luffytaro! Don't touch them!

293
00:23:28.270 --> 00:23:32.970
Stop! All of you!

294
00:23:32.970 --> 00:23:35.850
You idiot! You infected yourself!

295
00:23:52.570 --> 00:23:53.540
Is he stupid?!

296
00:23:58.060 --> 00:23:59.070
Stop already!

297
00:23:59.070 --> 00:24:00.420
You'll die!

298
00:24:01.460 --> 00:24:04.170
What are you doing, Master Luffytaro?!

299
00:24:11.310 --> 00:24:12.850
Sir Straw Hat!

300
00:24:17.100 --> 00:24:19.190
What "menace"?!

301
00:24:23.120 --> 00:24:26.860
"Its power is devastating"?!

302
00:24:28.180 --> 00:24:29.570
This disease...

303
00:24:30.170 --> 00:24:32.530
doesn't hurt me at all!

304
00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:35.810
Liar!

305
00:24:35.810 --> 00:24:37.750
Get away from them now!

306
00:24:37.750 --> 00:24:39.500
Luffy!

307
00:24:47.540 --> 00:24:52.470
Every samurai I've met is as tough as hell!

308
00:25:08.950 --> 00:25:12.060
But you guys...!

309
00:25:12.060 --> 00:25:15.490
Your spirit has been shattered!

310
00:25:21.080 --> 00:25:23.210
Living your "daily routine"?!

311
00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:28.630
They tell you what to do,
and you get your stupid dumplings...!

312
00:25:31.290 --> 00:25:36.560
They give you just enough to survive,
and you call that living?!

313
00:25:52.170 --> 00:25:53.700
Wake up!

314
00:25:54.530 --> 00:25:56.330
You know what that makes you?!

315
00:25:56.850 --> 00:25:58.780
Slaves!

316
00:26:06.600 --> 00:26:09.160
Big Bro and the others are okay!

317
00:26:09.160 --> 00:26:11.460
Are they really okay...?

318
00:26:14.570 --> 00:26:18.890
What's wrong with me
coming from another country?!

319
00:26:19.360 --> 00:26:23.020
What's wrong with a stranger
defending this land?!

320
00:26:38.380 --> 00:26:40.750
I made a promise!

321
00:26:43.410 --> 00:26:46.960
I promised... my friend...

322
00:26:46.960 --> 00:26:50.710
who gave me her own food in Kuri!

323
00:26:51.450 --> 00:26:56.510
I will make this a country
where everyone can eat their fill!

324
00:27:01.400 --> 00:27:03.100
I'm gonna make this normal for you!

325
00:27:04.640 --> 00:27:07.660
Before we leave this country,

326
00:27:07.660 --> 00:27:11.480
I'll make it a place where you can
eat as much as you want!

327
00:27:14.880 --> 00:27:16.910
Big Bro...

328
00:27:16.910 --> 00:27:19.240
I'm gonna keep that promise...!

329
00:27:20.710 --> 00:27:25.210
If I don't... this country will be...

330
00:27:25.210 --> 00:27:27.750
an eternal hell!

331
00:27:36.130 --> 00:27:38.490
I heard about Oden.

332
00:27:39.200 --> 00:27:41.180
He was amazing!

333
00:27:42.710 --> 00:27:48.400
But on the day Kaido
killed him twenty years ago...

334
00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:52.070
this country stopped moving forward!

335
00:27:57.060 --> 00:28:02.050
We came to defeat Kaido!

336
00:28:03.150 --> 00:28:08.120
We don't need allies who just get our way!

337
00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:16.380
So, now's the time for you to decide!

338
00:28:17.090 --> 00:28:18.780
Are you with us?!

339
00:28:19.740 --> 00:28:22.180
Or with Kaido?!

340
00:28:31.120 --> 00:28:32.520
Are you serious?

341
00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:45.820
You'd give us...

342
00:28:47.330 --> 00:28:49.090
another chance?

343
00:29:04.520 --> 00:29:06.120
He's won their hearts!

344
00:29:07.810 --> 00:29:10.100
What a commanding presence!

345
00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:13.310
We've got a problem.

346
00:29:14.300 --> 00:29:17.280
He's gone and stirred their hearts.

347
00:29:17.750 --> 00:29:22.370
But if I fire a shot right now
while their guard is down,

348
00:29:22.370 --> 00:29:24.780
they'll all panic...

349
00:29:25.380 --> 00:29:27.910
flipping the situation in our favor.

350
00:29:28.540 --> 00:29:33.380
I'll scatter 200 plague rounds
worth of the virus

351
00:29:33.380 --> 00:29:35.340
using this plague shot!

352
00:29:38.920 --> 00:29:42.430
Eat a big bowl of elephant snot!

353
00:29:43.890 --> 00:29:46.370
No way, Warden! That's too much!

354
00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:50.350
No, please don't!

355
00:29:54.750 --> 00:29:57.550
Hey, Babanuki looks like he's
about to fire something over here.

356
00:29:57.550 --> 00:29:58.480
What?!

357
00:30:00.950 --> 00:30:02.160
It's too late!

358
00:30:08.790 --> 00:30:12.740
Elephant Achoo!

359
00:30:20.170 --> 00:30:21.410
What?!

360
00:30:23.680 --> 00:30:25.140
What?! What?! What?!

361
00:30:28.380 --> 00:30:31.430
I had to. I saw a pretty bad future.

362
00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:46.660
Warden Babanuki!

363
00:30:46.660 --> 00:30:49.170
Warden!

364
00:30:56.890 --> 00:30:58.210
What a...

365
00:31:00.590 --> 00:31:02.840
formidable man he is...!

366
00:31:05.050 --> 00:31:06.390
The rest is up to you.

367
00:31:15.380 --> 00:31:16.900
We'll handle it!

368
00:31:16.900 --> 00:31:19.820
Hey, wait! You better remember!

369
00:31:20.290 --> 00:31:22.740
What happens if you defy the guards?!

370
00:31:22.740 --> 00:31:26.160
First, we cut off both your arms!

371
00:31:26.160 --> 00:31:28.240
We know, and we don't care.

372
00:31:28.240 --> 00:31:32.500
We've already decided to revolt!

373
00:31:34.960 --> 00:31:36.930
This is payback for all these years...!

374
00:31:36.930 --> 00:31:38.500
Here we go!

375
00:31:37.980 --> 00:31:38.500
Yeah!

376
00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:52.640
Eight days until the final battle...

377
00:31:54.290 --> 00:31:57.600
Unbeknownst to the enemy's main army...

378
00:32:06.030 --> 00:32:06.320
<b>conquered</b>

379
00:32:06.200 --> 00:32:10.650
<b>been conquered</b>

380
00:32:06.570 --> 00:32:06.820
<b>has</b>

381
00:32:06.610 --> 00:32:06.700
<b>been</b>

382
00:32:06.690 --> 00:32:06.860
<b>Udon</b>

383
00:32:06.820 --> 00:32:07.480
<b>Udon has</b>

384
00:32:07.480 --> 00:32:10.650
<b>has</b>
<b>Udon</b>

385
00:32:08.160 --> 00:32:10.660
Udon has been conquered!

386
00:32:11.310 --> 00:32:15.200
You did it, Sir Straw Hat!

387
00:32:24.810 --> 00:32:28.180
You've brought us quite the reinforcement,

388
00:32:28.970 --> 00:32:30.930
Kin'emon!
